snippet.textDisplay: What a coincidence, I'm watching the New York Red Bulls take on FC Dallas and I find out that you posted a Nintendo World Cup song! This is one of my favorite NES games and I want them to make more soccer games like this. But for my money, the best music is the second World Cup match music (the one that plays against Russia, Spain, and England). Gets you so pumped up!
